{"tid":847531,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"長毛：黃毓民當日叫人焦土，何解今日叫人支持馮檢基？！","createTime":"2018-10-04T08:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T03:38:28.000Z","uid":49388,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"498f56eafad5209a3a252ad565bd80b783a6f7ed","tid":847531,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:49:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UFnvxfCrvA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUFnvxfCrvA8&d=8BteI%2Bf9ky9hy%2B9tl%2BrAfS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e0345d21\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UFnvxfCrvA8</a><br />\n長毛：<br />\n黃毓民當年鬧馮檢基出賣民主運動，鬧基哥係人唔似人鬼唔似鬼，之前仲叫人焦土，但今日就一反常態叫人投馮檢基？ 黃毓民咪就係搞到自己人唔似人鬼唔鬼Lor！<br />\n<br />\n馮撿基好意思話人不民主？你當年參加臨立會點計？"},{"pid":"b9384e6db84cfd14e8db98bd67477c6c374d9377","tid":847531,"uid":28181,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"教主對事不對人，唔係你d泛民私怨大過天，為左趕教主出議會支持修訂議事規則。"},{"pid":"5b82f0c68777b94c47950542c930d717730b6dd0","tid":847531,"uid":33477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b9384e6db84cfd14e8db98bd67477c6c374d9377","tid":847531,"uid":28181,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"教主對事不對人，唔係你d泛民私怨大過天，為左趕教主出議會支持修訂議事規則。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bLcEUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bLcEUh.jpg&h=366c69f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0078fd33644df7be4c0a8dc6c7d4d9ab99a9ba44","tid":847531,"uid":128261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"馮檢基雖然同樣反泛民大台，但係佢立場同本土派南轅北轍，「本土派」撐佢無問題，但如果選舉同佢站台既肯定係人渣政棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d8480dcc747ea62e16d8bb00ac007d0416ee50","tid":847531,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9384e6db84cfd14e8db98bd67477c6c374d93